
Package: scBridge
Title: Seamless Conversion Between Seurat and AnnData Objects
Version: 0.2.2
Authors@R: person("Zhijun", "Feng", email = "xiaoqqjun@sina.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1813-1669"))
Description: Provides reliable bidirectional conversion between Seurat (R) and
    AnnData (Python) objects via intermediate files. Bypasses known bugs in
    SeuratDisk and MuDataSeurat by using a safe MTX + CSV intermediate format
    with automatic temporary directory management. Compatible with Seurat v4
    and v5.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
